<div class="adv-richtext" data-cs-capture>
  {{ section.settings.bridge_text }}
</div>

<div class="adv-cta-block" id="cta1">
  <a href="{{ section.settings.cta_url }}?utm_source=kesehatanwanita_blog&utm_medium=advertorial_cta&utm_campaign={{ section.settings.utm_campaign | default: 'moringa_discovery_launch' | url_encode }}&utm_content={{ section.settings.utm_content | default: 'mid-article' | url_encode }}"
   class="adv-cta-button"
   data-meta-event="Lead"
   data-meta-product-name="{{ section.settings.meta_product_name }}"
   data-meta-content-id="{{ section.settings.meta_content_id }}"
   data-meta-value="{{ section.settings.meta_product_value }}"
   data-meta-currency="{{ shop.currency }}"
   data-meta-category="Blog to Store Conversion"
   data-meta-cta-position="mid-article"
   id="meta-cta-trigger-1">
  {{ section.settings.cta_text }}
</a>
  {% if section.settings.cta_subtext != blank %}
    <div class="adv-cta-sub" data-cs-capture>{{ section.settings.cta_subtext }}</div>
  {% endif %}
  {% if section.blocks.size > 0 %}
    <div class="adv-cta-badges">
      {% for block in section.blocks %}
        <span {{ block.shopify_attributes }} data-cs-capture>{{ block.settings.badge_label }}</span>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</div>

{% render 'meta-cta-tracking' %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Advertorial Bridge + CTA",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "bridge_text",
      "label": "Bridge Text",
      "default": "<p>While most brands I've researched source their moringa from third parties and focus only on nutrition or only on skincare, I came across a small Indonesian brand that takes a different approach entirely. Treelogy grows its own moringa on their organic-certified farm in Bali and processes it in their own BPOM-registered facility. From soil to product — everything under one roof.</p><p>That matters more than most people realize. Some of the nutrients in moringa are so fragile that if you can't see how it's made, it's probably being made in a way that destroys them. Treelogy publishes their process openly — which, after weeks of researching this market, I can tell you is rare.</p><p>And the best part? They offer a Starter Pack that lets you try the capsules and powder in smaller sizes — so you can find which format fits your daily routine — along with the seed oil for skin and hair. It's their full inside-and-outside protocol in one box. They're running it at a lower price this month with free shipping while stock lasts.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "cta_url",
      "label": "CTA Button URL"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cta_text",
      "label": "CTA Button Text",
      "default": "See the Starter Pack →"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cta_subtext",
      "label": "CTA Subtext",
      "default": "Free shipping for readers of this article · 30-day protocol"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "UTM Tracking"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "utm_campaign",
      "label": "UTM Campaign",
      "default": "moringa_discovery_launch",
      "info": "Identifies which campaign (e.g. moringa_discovery_launch, menopause_discovery_launch)"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "utm_content",
      "label": "UTM Content",
      "default": "mid-article",
      "info": "Identifies CTA position & version (e.g. mid-article, mid-article-v2)"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Meta Pixel Tracking"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "meta_product_name",
      "label": "Product Name (for Meta)",
      "default": "Discovery Pack",
      "info": "Sent as content_name in the Lead event"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "meta_product_value",
      "label": "Product Value (for Meta)",
      "default": "299000",
      "info": "Numeric value sent with the Lead event"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "meta_content_id",
      "label": "Product ID / SKU (for Meta)",
      "default": "OMC-90-001",
      "info": "Must match the ID used in your Meta Catalog"
    }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "badge",
      "name": "Trust Badge",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "badge_label",
          "label": "Badge Label",
          "default": "BPOM Certified"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Advertorial Bridge + CTA",
      "blocks": [
        { "type": "badge", "settings": { "badge_label": "BPOM Certified" } },
        { "type": "badge", "settings": { "badge_label": "Halal" } },
        { "type": "badge", "settings": { "badge_label": "100% Organic" } },
        { "type": "badge", "settings": { "badge_label": "Lab-Verified" } }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
